# School of AI, Data & Autonomous Systems

## Purpose
Trains students to design, evaluate, and deploy AI-enabled systems responsibly, with strong foundations in data, software practice, and applied ethics.

## Scope
- AI fundamentals, data engineering, LLM operations, agentic systems, evaluation and safety
- Credentials: certificates, BS/MS tracks
- Delivery: online/hybrid; project-based

## Distinctives
- Portfolio-first outcomes (deployments, audits, evaluations)
- Applied AI governance and documentation standards
- Capstone: agent/tool deployment with evaluation report